projects.name: Pizza Order and Tracking App
projects.description: Real-time pizza order tracker app using NodeJs, Express, and MongoDB. In this project, I have built a real-time online pizza order app using Node.Js, Express.Js, and MongoDB. Using tailwind CSS for frontend as a CSS framework and will be using EJS template engine as well as using socket.io for real-time communication. Using this app we will be able to order a pizza and get real-time notifications about pizza status.
